
  Exploud    Normal Type Pokémon

  EXPLOUD triggers earthquakes 
  with the tremors it creates by 
  bellowing.  If Exploud violently 
  inhales from the ports on its 
  body, it’s a sign that it is 
  preparing to let loose a huge 
  bellow. 
	   Evolution Chain
